stimulus:
Now you will be able to record a test sound
and then play it back to check that the audio has been captured clearly.

After you press the "Start the recording check" button,
you will be need to approve the browser's request to use the mic.

Then the browser will record audio for 2 seconds.

You will then see an audio player and you will be able to play back your recording.

You can re-record as many times as necessary to ensure that,
during the test, the audio will be captured clearly.
Press the "Start" button to start the audio recording test.
